// ===================================================================
//  test_union_find_pure.hexa -- coverage for union_find_pure.hexa
//
//  20+ distinct test scenarios covering:
//    - basic creation, find, union
//    - transitive connectivity
//    - component counting
//    - self-union (idempotent)
//    - duplicate union
//    - large chains
//    - single / empty UF
//    - star topology, path topology
//    - root consistency after compression
//
